<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="<%= show_user_bg %>">
  <head>
    <title>Tubalr - A simple tool for enjoying music videos!</title>
    <meta property="og:image" content="http://www.tubalr.com/assets/facebook-meta-logo.png"/>
    <META NAME="Description" CONTENT="Tubalr is a simple way to enjoy great music videos.">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=PT+Sans:400,700,800,400italic,700italic", "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,300,700,600,800", "application" %>

    <script>
      var _gaq = _gaq || [];
      _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-16656461-3']);
      _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);
      (function() {
      var ga = document.createElement('script'); ga.type = 'text/javascript'; ga.async = true;
      ga.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://ssl' : 'http://www') + '.google-analytics.com/ga.js';
      var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);
      })();
    </script>
    <%= javascript_include_tag  "http://connect.facebook.net/en_US/all.js", "http://connect.soundcloud.com/sdk.js", "application" %>
    <!--[if lt IE 9]><script src="//html5shiv.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script><![endif]-->
    <%= javascript_tag do %>
      User.init({
        id:           <%= current_user.id %>,
        username:     '<%= escape_javascript(current_user.username) %>',
        bannedVideos: <%= array_or_string_for_javascript(current_user.banned_videos.map(&:video_id)) %>
      });
    <% end if user_signed_in? %>

    <%= csrf_meta_tag %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="fb-root"></div>

    <div id="main">
      <div id="inner-main">
        <div id="notices">
          <%= "<aside class='flash-msg'>#{flash[:alert]}</aside>".html_safe   if !flash[:alert].nil?  %>
          <%= "<aside class='flash-msg'>#{flash[:notice]}</aside>".html_safe  if !flash[:notice].nil? %>
        </div>

        <header id="main-header">
          <h1 id="logo">
            <a href='/' class="tooltip" original-title="Pronounced: tuba-ler">tubalr</a>
          </h1>

          <nav id="main-nav">
            <%= link_to('about', '#', { :class => 'about-tubalr' }) %>
            <% if user_signed_in? %>
              <%= link_to('my profile', "/#{current_user.username}/profile") %>
              <%= link_to('settings', '/users/edit') %>
              <%= link_to('logout', destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete) %>
            <% else %>
              <%= link_to('sign up', '/users/sign_up') %>
              <%= link_to('login', '/users/sign_in') %>
            <% end %>
          </nav>

          <%= render :partial => 'search_form' if !@dj %>
        </header>

        <%= render :partial => 'player' %>

        <%= yield %>

        <aside class="social">
          <iframe src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http://www.facebook.com/pages/Tubalr/154359441249128&amp;send=false&amp;layout=button_count&amp;width=80&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=like&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;font&amp;height=21" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; height:21px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/tubalr" class="twitter-follow-button" data-show-count="true">Follow @tubalr</a>
          <script>!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js";fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document,"script","twitter-wjs");</script>
        </aside>

        <a id="echo" href="http://the.echonest.com/" target="_blank"><img src="/assets/echo.gif" width="60" height="50"/></a>

        <div id="about-tubalr">
          <p>
            Pronounced: tuba-ler
          </p>

          <h3>Reddit</h3>
          <p>
            Have feedback, feature requests, or bugs? Want to share a custom playlist or whatever else you may think of? Head on over to <a href="http://www.reddit.com/r/tubalr" target="_blank">/r/tubalr</a>.
          <p>

          <h3>Blog</h3>
          <p>
            Checkout Tubalr's <%= link_to('blog', 'http://www.tubalr.tumblr.com/', :target => '_blank') %> for updates.
          </p>

          <h3>GitHub</h3>
          <p>
            Tubalr's full source can be found on <a href="https://github.com/cjstewart88/tubalr" target="_blank">github</a>,
            feel free to send a PR or submit an issue!
          </p>

          <h3>Why was this built?</h3>
          <p>
            Tubalr is an app that was crafted out of curiosity and passion, Sept 12th 2010. I
            released it into the wild and have been iterating ever since. I built Tubalr because
            I kept running across great high quality videos wishing I had a simple app to play those
            videos back to back, while working or doing other things.
          </p>

          <p>
            I mentioned that I've been tweaking Tubalr since its creation, and thats largely due to
            the amazing feedback and support given by its supporters and users. So with that said, if
            you have ANY feedback or just wanna chat... please shoot an e-mail to
            <a href='mailto:listen.to.tubalr@gmail.com'>listen.to.tubalr@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>

          <h3>Who built it?</h3>
          <p>
            Me, <a href="http://www.twitter.com/codyjackstewart" target="_blank">Cody Stewart</a>, I'm the
            founder and crafter of Tubalr. There's also been a few open source contributions via <a href="https://github.com/cjstewart88/Tubalr/contributors" target="_blank">github</a>.
          </p>

          <h3>Donate</h3>
          <p>
            Tubalr is run with time, effort, and care... and will continue to, as long as there is interest
            and support behind the idea. Regardless of monetary backing, Tubalr will continue to run as long as it can.
          </p>
          <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">
            <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_s-xclick">
            <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="VLGMMSXGJVV56">
            <input type="submit" value="Donate">
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
